trans-unit.source: FastTrack Center Benefit for Intune
trans-unit.target: FastTrack Center Benefit for Intune

trans-unit.source: You can use the service benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Microsoft Intune in an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: You can use the service benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Microsoft Intune in an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: The service benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.
trans-unit.target: The service benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.

trans-unit.source: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the service benefit.
trans-unit.target: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the service benefit.

trans-unit.source: To learn about the onboarding process as well as roles and responsibilities, see <link><linkText>FastTrack Center Benefit Process for Intune</linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: Eligible services
trans-unit.target: Eligible services

trans-unit.source: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.
trans-unit.target: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.

trans-unit.source: Microsoft will attempt to contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft will attempt to contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.
trans-unit.target: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.

trans-unit.source: To request assistance, sign in to the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link>, go to the dashboard, select your company name, click the Offers tab, and click the Request Assistance button to request assistance for Microsoft Intune, Azure Active Directory Premium, or Azure Rights Management Premium.
trans-unit.target: To request assistance, sign in to the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link>, go to the dashboard, select your company name, click the Offers tab, and click the Request Assistance button to request assistance for Microsoft Intune, Azure Active Directory Premium, or Azure Rights Management Premium.

trans-unit.source: Customers can opt-in to the onboarding process once per each eligible Microsoft online service.
trans-unit.target: Customers can opt-in to the onboarding process once per each eligible Microsoft online service.
